history.content: In terms of workload, I definitely would say 170 is heaver than 188 due to the pretty tough weekly problem sets. 188 homeworks are mostly completion based, and the projects are partner and do not take too long. If you're looking for a lighter 4th class, then this is definitely a better choice considering the other tough classes in 61C, 7B, and 134. In terms of material, I think both classes are interesting, but 170 is more fundamentally important imo because it has a lot of generally important ideas that are valuable in interviews and in CS. 188 might be valuable if you're interested in getting into AI research.
Right now I have 61C+Physics 7B+STAT134. Which option would be more reasonable? Thanks :)
history.subject: Should I go with 170 or 188
